OL,3,CHealth officials monitoring Welsh
OL,4,Cresidents linked with hantavirus
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FHealth officials are monitoring a
OL,8,F"small number" of Welsh residents who
OL,9,Fhave been linked to the hantavirus
OL,10,Foutbreak aboard a cruise ship, Public
OL,11,FHealth Wales (PHW) has confirmed.
OL,13,FThe organisation has said that the
OL,14,Fpeople affected are well and are not
OL,15,Fshowing symptoms, but will be self-
OL,16,Fisolating and regularly assessed.
OL,18,FThose who are self-isolating were
OL,19,Fconfirmed to be on board the Dutch
OL,20,Fcruise ship MV Hondius, or had contact
OL,21,Fwith those who were.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,468,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1778864757
OL,3,CHealth officials monitoring Welsh
OL,4,Cresidents linked with hantavirus
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FIt comes as three passengers died
OL,8,Fafter the outbreak of hantavirus
OL,9,Fonboard, with 11 cases reported
OL,10,Faltogether.
OL,12,FPublic Health Wales says it is working
OL,13,Fwith Welsh Government, the UK Health
OL,14,FSecurity Agency (UKHSA), Welsh health
OL,15,Fboards and local authorities to
OL,16,Frespond to the outbreak and to "take
OL,17,Fthe appropriate action."
OL,19,FThere are currently no known cases of
OL,20,Fhantavirus in Wales.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,468,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1778864757
OL,3,CHealth officials monitoring Welsh
OL,4,Cresidents linked with hantavirus
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FThere were 22 Brits evacuated from the
OL,8,Fhantavirus-stricken cruise ship.
OL,10,FThey will have spent 72 hours
OL,11,Fisolating at Arrowe Park Hospital on
OL,12,FMerseyside, and were set to start
OL,13,Fleaving quarantine on Wednesday to
OL,14,Fself-isolate for a further 42 days at
OL,15,Fhome or in other accommodation.
OL,17,FPublic Health Wales says the risk to
OL,18,Fthe general public is very low.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
