OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1778864757
OL,3,CHealth officials monitoring Welsh
OL,4,Cresidents linked with hantavirus
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FThe World Health Organization (WHO)
OL,8,Fsays it is continuing to monitor the
OL,9,Fsituation.
OL,11,FIn a statement, Consultant in Public
OL,12,FHealth for Public Health Wales, Joanna
OL,13,FGarner, said: "We are committed to
OL,14,Frespecting the privacy of every
OL,15,Findividual involved in a public health
OL,16,Fresponse.
OL,26,@uD@OOU
