OL,3,CHealth officials monitoring Welsh
OL,4,Cresidents linked with hantavirus
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,F"Information about those individuals
OL,8,Fis handled in strict confidence, and
OL,9,Fit would be inappropriate for us to
OL,10,Fcomment on personal details relating
OL,11,Fto any specific person."
OL,13,FWhat is hantavirus?
OL,15,FHantaviruses are a group of viruses
OL,16,Fthat are normally carried by rodents,
OL,17,Fsuch as rats, mice and voles.
OL,26,@sD@XO]
