OL,3,CHealth officials monitoring Welsh
OL,4,Cresidents linked with hantavirus
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FThey are present throughout the world
OL,8,Fand can cause a range of diseases in
OL,9,Fhumans ranging from mild, flu-like
OL,10,Fillness to severe respiratory illness
OL,11,For haemorrhagic disease with kidney
OL,12,Fissues.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/8
